entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You managed to blame Lady Valarian for the lab assistant's death.
entries.journal_entry_description: Blame the whole thing on Lady Valarian.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Travel to the Lucky Despot in Mos Eisley.  Once there, check in with Bib Fortuna.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: So you have tracked the killer back to the Lucky Despot?  This must be the dirty work of the Valarians!  Send a message to Lady Valarian from Jabba. Kill the assassin in the Lucky Despot.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Find Lady Valarian in the Lucky Despot and somehow solve this issue. BEWARE - This will probably end badly.
entries.task02_start_message: You hear a secret door in the room open.
